Note for your website
For production use, I recommend storing links in this format instead:
https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=PLACE_NAME

Example:
https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Times+Square+New+York

This is Google's officially supported deep-link format and works better on desktop, Android, and iPhone than the shorter maps.google.com/?q= URLs.

